- Over here.

33:00.203 --> 33:01.574
- Close the door!

33:01.610 --> 33:03.084
- Ah!

33:03.119 --> 33:04.216
- Oh, no!

33:05.432 --> 33:08.507
- Shoot this motherfucker!

33:10.561 --> 33:11.532
Kill it!
Kill it!

33:11.566 --> 33:12.972
Shoot it!
Shoot it!

33:15.589 --> 33:17.291
- Shoot it!

33:17.332 --> 33:18.395
God!

33:25.109 --> 33:26.948
- Right now, get away!
Get away!

