and we wouldn't even know.

34:08.922 --> 34:10.020
Fuck out of the way.

34:10.062 --> 34:12.702
I'll finish him off.

34:12.743 --> 34:14.275
- Ugh!

34:14.320 --> 34:15.987
- Ah!
Oh...

34:16.029 --> 34:17.467
Fuck.

34:19.313 --> 34:20.947
