34:50.690 --> 34:53.135
- This is your fault.

34:53.170 --> 34:55.342
You were supposed to bring
a captive back here.

35:03.261 --> 35:05.741
- Sacha.

35:05.775 --> 35:08.220
All quiet here?

35:11.943 --> 35:14.114
- You're an educated man, Dima.

35:16.199 --> 35:19.583
What do you think
is going on here?

35:19.620 --> 35:21.255
- I am...

35:21.296 --> 35:23.707
not sure.

35:23.743 --> 35:26.885
