of something like this...

35:35.843 --> 35:39.456
Sewing dead people together

35:39.498 --> 35:43.315
and giving them knives
for hands.

35:43.353 --> 35:45.330
It's insane.

35:45.364 --> 35:48.140
- Or brilliant.

35:50.024 --> 35:51.520
No, Dima.

35:53.209 --> 35:54.705
It's insane.

36:07.154 --> 36:10.971
We'll move in the morning,

36:11.008 --> 36:15.191
and then we'll find
this Tiger Bear 3-0-3.

36:16.406 --> 36:18.108
- They're dead,

36:18.149 --> 36:19.177
and we will be too

36:19.221 --> 36:21.165
