any longer.

36:24.987 --> 36:26.187
- Sacha, go down!

36:26.227 --> 36:27.324
Sacha!

36:38.128 --> 36:39.499
- Go around!

36:39.535 --> 36:40.632
Sacha!

36:43.525 --> 36:45.160
- Hands up!
Hands in the air!

36:45.201 --> 36:46.263
Come on!

36:46.306 --> 36:47.370
Hold your fire!

36:47.413 --> 36:50.053
Hold your fire!

36:50.095 --> 36:51.124
- No, no!

36:51.167 --> 36:52.325
- Against the wall!

36:52.366 --> 36:53.989
Over there!

36:54.031 --> 36:55.552
- No, that is a girl!

36:55.596 --> 36:56.719
That's a girl!

36:56.761 --> 36:59.724
That's a girl!
- No, no, no, no!

36:59.758 --> 37:00.847
- Get over here!

37:00.889 --> 37:02.819
- Vasja!
- No, no, no, no!

37:02.854 --> 37:04.182
- Vasja!

37:06.017 --> 37:08.639
- Enough!
Enough!

37:08.680 --> 37:10.644
Where are the Russians?
- Please...

37:10.677 --> 37:11.869
- Where are the Russians?

37:11.910 --> 37:13.534
- You are Russians, no?

37:13.575 --> 37:16.366
- There where other Russians
here.

37:16.404 --> 37:17.460
Yesterday!

37:17.503 --> 37:18.966
- I... I don't know.

37:19.001 --> 37:21.294
We've been hiding.

37:21.331 --> 37:23.850
- Just the four of you?

37:23.895 --> 37:26.358
- Everyone else was killed
or ran.

37:26.393 --> 37:27.448
It was a massacre.

37:27.491 --> 37:29.115
- Who killed them?

37:29.156 --> 37:31.244
- The undead ones.

37:31.287 --> 37:34.613
Listen, the gunshots
and your firelight...

37:34.650 --> 37:36.307
We must hide
before they come looking.

37:36.348 --> 37:37.971
- Where do they come from?

37:38.012 --> 37:40.305
- Dima, leave this to me!

37:42.241 --> 37:43.898
How many were there?

37:43.938 --> 37:44.993
- We don't know.

37:45.037 --> 37:46.865
He keeps making more.

37:46.902 --> 37:48.525
We must hide now.
Please.

37:48.566 --> 37:50.164
- This is bullshit.
Let's just kill them.

37:50.165 --> 37:51.458
- No...
<i>Du darfst mich schiessen!</i>

37:51.496 --> 37:52.654
<i>- Nein, nein!
Bitte, bitte!</i>

37:52.695 --> 37:54.658
<i>Du darfst mich erschiessen
statt ihr.</i>

37:54.692 --> 37:56.213
- What did he say?

37:57.921 --> 37:59.886
Fritz says it's okay
if you shoot him.

37:59.919 --> 38:01.383
He'd rather be shot
by a real man

38:01.418 --> 38:04.710
than ripped apart
by those things out there.

38:04.748 --> 38:08.539
- Let's just kill them.
Keep the girl.

38:08.576 --> 38:10.199
Come here.

38:10.240 --> 38:11.864
- No, no, no, no.

38:11.905 --> 38:14.095
I am a trained nurse, ja?

38:14.136 --> 38:15.396
Look!
I can help your friend.

38:15.434 --> 38:17.330
- A trained nurse?

38:17.366 --> 38:18.592
- I can help your friend.

38:24.257 --> 38:26.516
I will help your comrade, ja?

38:29.584 --> 38:32.047
- Here.
Just breathe.

38:32.082 --> 38:35.203
Vanya, breathe.

38:35.244 --> 38:38.365
Well, can you get it off?

38:38.407 --> 38:39.871
- I don't know.

38:39.906 --> 38:41.529
- You get it off,

38:41.570 --> 38:43.761
and we'll let you live.

38:43.802 --> 38:45.923
Deal?

38:45.965 --> 38:48.985
- I...
I can try.

38:49.028 --> 38:50.185
- You heard him, bitch.

38:50.226 --> 38:51.248
Get on with it.

38:51.292 --> 38:53.255
- Okay, Vanya, what we'll do...

38:54.356 --> 38:56.285
- Breathe.

38:57.718 --> 39:00.011
- Slowly!
Slowly!

39:00.049 --> 39:01.411
Breathe!

39:02.779 --> 39:03.800
- Ivan...

39:07.340 --> 39:08.497
- Ivan, look at the nurse.

39:10.103 --> 39:11.760
- Don't move.

39:19.126 --> 39:22.486
I'm sorry.
I'm sorry.

39:22.522 --> 39:25.609
- Well,
that was fucking useless.

39:25.652 --> 39:27.173
- No, no!

39:27.217 --> 39:28.238
We must work together.

39:28.282 --> 39:29.871
We're all human.

39:29.913 --> 39:31.038
Please don't hurt me.

39:31.078 --> 39:33.008
Please!
No, no!

39:35.805 --> 39:36.828
- Vasja!

39:36.872 --> 39:37.872
- No! No!

39:37.904 --> 39:38.960
- Vasja!

39:39.002 --> 39:41.091
- Ah!
- Enough!

39:45.328 --> 39:46.328
- Alexei!

39:48.991 --> 39:52.078
- Shoot that thing, somebody!

39:52.121 --> 39:54.583
- Shoot it, Sacha!
Shoot it!

39:57.314 --> 39:58.642
Alexei, hold on!

40:08.501 --> 40:09.556
- Shoot it!

40:11.397 --> 40:13.951
Shoot it!

40:13.994 --> 40:16.045
Someone stop it!
Stop it!

40:16.087 --> 40:17.571
Sacha!
Sacha, follow me!

40:17.616 --> 40:20.073
Sacha!
- Dima, careful!

40:20.107 --> 40:21.828
Where is it?

40:27.948 --> 40:29.002
- Shoot!

40:35.423 --> 40:36.578
- Shit!

40:50.174 --> 40:51.174
Sacha!

40:51.204 --> 40:52.326
Sergei!

40:53.430 --> 40:55.219
- I'll get the camera!

40:55.257 --> 40:57.941
I got it.
I got it.

40:57.982 --> 41:00.235
I got the camera.

41:00.274 --> 41:02.325
Dima, I got the camera!

41:02.367 --> 41:03.522
- Ahh!

41:03.563 --> 41:05.715
- Grenade!
Get down!

41:12.401 --> 41:15.380
- Dima!
Dima!

41:20.873 --> 41:22.526
- Are you all right?

41:25.557 --> 41:27.347
- My eyes...
- Sacha.

41:27.384 --> 41:29.343
Sacha, give me the camera.

41:29.377 --> 41:30.771
- Take it.

41:30.806 --> 41:32.200
- Here!

41:32.234 --> 41:34.023
Down the hole!
Quickly!

41:36.620 --> 41:39.543
- Eva!
Eva!

41:39.578 --> 41:41.469
Eva!

41:41.504 --> 41:43.555
- No, no, this way.
- This way, Dima!

41:43.597 --> 41:45.023
Sacha!
Dima!

41:46.953 --> 41:48.380
- Come on, Vasja!

41:48.415 --> 41:49.841
Grenade!
- Hey!

42:14.295 --> 42:16.413
- Does anyone read me?
Over.

42:18.282 --> 42:20.139
We are trapped.
We can't hold out much longer.

42:20.176 --> 42:22.928
Our position
is 51-17-28 north

42:22.966 --> 42:26.250
by 13-22-04 east.

42:26.288 --> 42:28.111
Do you read me?
Over.

42:29.644 --> 42:31.762
- I don't fucking believe this.

42:31.804 --> 42:33.389
- Sergei.

42:33.432 --> 42:35.550
Comrade.

42:35.592 --> 42:36.712
Let me explain...

42:42.700 --> 42:44.320
- What's going on?

42:44.362 --> 42:47.648
- Why don't you ask
Comrade Dima?

42:47.684 --> 42:50.640
- What?

42:50.674 --> 42:52.328
- Tell them...

42:52.368 --> 42:53.988
before I blow
your fucking brains out.

42:54.029 --> 42:55.029
- You don't understand.

42:55.060 --> 42:56.543
- Tell them!

43:00.508 --> 43:03.465
- There's no Tiger Bear 3-0-3.

43:03.499 --> 43:04.959
- I don't get it.

43:04.993 --> 43:07.610
- Here.

43:07.651 --> 43:10.302
It's a radio-jammer.

43:10.341 --> 43:11.463
I couldn't understand

43:11.505 --> 43:12.943
why we were getting
no signal before.

43:12.967 --> 43:15.424
This is why.

43:15.459 --> 43:19.933
Our comrade here
was blocking us,

43:19.977 --> 43:21.767
cutting us off from Mother.

43:21.805 --> 43:24.919
- And I was carrying
the fucking thing!

43:24.960 --> 43:27.679
- He could use it
to transmit the message

43:27.718 --> 43:30.267
from his pack to the radio
and...

43:30.310 --> 43:31.601
- And lead us here.

43:31.638 --> 43:32.759
So there is no...

43:32.801 --> 43:33.888
- No Tiger Bear,

43:33.930 --> 43:36.219
no Russian soldiers
needing our help.

43:36.256 --> 43:39.178
- Fucking bastard!

43:39.213 --> 43:40.232
- Oof!

43:40.276 --> 43:41.432
Ah!

43:43.532 --> 43:44.654
- Wait, Vasja.

43:44.695 --> 43:46.484
Don't kill him yet.

43:46.523 --> 43:49.308
First I want to know why.

43:49.346 --> 43:52.733
- We are not going anywhere.

43:55.026 --> 43:56.680
Not going anywhere.

43:58.416 --> 44:00.328
- That fritz must know the way.
We'll follow him.

44:00.343 --> 44:03.299
- That fucking old fascist?

44:03.333 --> 44:04.953
- You don't understand.

44:06.755 --> 44:09.213
We are not leaving.

44:09.246 --> 44:10.299
That's an order.

44:10.342 --> 44:11.396
- An order?

44:11.440 --> 44:12.992
I'm going to cut his balls off...

44:13.034 --> 44:14.054
- Here, here, here, here.

44:14.097 --> 44:15.717
- Oof!

44:15.758 --> 44:17.378
- Read this document.

44:17.420 --> 44:20.240
I'm a full captain,
your superior officer.

44:22.469 --> 44:24.107
I have a list
of every man in this squad's

44:24.131 --> 44:25.920
family and loved ones.

44:25.958 --> 44:28.575
If something happens to me...

44:28.616 --> 44:29.907
- What?

44:29.944 --> 44:31.768
- You know what will happen
to them.

44:41.772 --> 44:42.791
- Right.

44:42.835 --> 44:44.160
- Dima...

44:46.689 --> 44:48.173
Tell me...

44:49.812 --> 44:52.951
Why didn't you just tell us?

44:52.993 --> 44:55.299
Huh?

44:55.338 --> 44:57.471
Why the trick?

44:57.512 --> 45:00.321
- This is a top secret mission.

45:00.360 --> 45:02.163
The bureau was afraid
there might be a leak.

45:02.201 --> 45:03.673
- So you let us come unprepared?

45:03.708 --> 45:05.841
- No, I did not know
the exact nature

45:05.884 --> 45:07.585
of the work
that the doctor was working on.

45:07.625 --> 45:10.433
- He's not a doctor.

45:10.471 --> 45:12.274
He's a madman.

45:12.312 --> 45:16.319
- My orders are to capture him,
if possible.

45:16.364 --> 45:17.461
If not, kill him.

45:17.503 --> 45:18.632
- Capture?

45:18.675 --> 45:20.170
What does
the glorious motherland...

45:20.215 --> 45:21.916
- Listen!
- Want with that madman?

45:21.956 --> 45:23.931
- Listen to me!

45:23.966 --> 45:25.437
This is none of your business.

45:25.472 --> 45:27.972
You do your job;
you go home safe and sound.

45:28.017 --> 45:29.146
Do you understand?

45:29.188 --> 45:30.594
- Is there even film
in that camera?

45:30.596 --> 45:31.897
- Yes, yes.
The film is real.

45:31.934 --> 45:33.098
I need a record of everything

45:33.106 --> 45:34.636
just in case
we cannot take him alive.

45:34.680 --> 45:37.156
Now, Fritz,

45:37.192 --> 45:38.595
we are going
to the doctor's base,

45:38.632 --> 45:40.971
and you...
You're taking us there.

45:41.008 --> 45:42.241
Which way?

46:11.713 --> 46:14.213
- This is the lift
up to the church.

46:18.276 --> 46:21.083
- If these things
are a Nazi weapon,

46:21.121 --> 46:23.598
they've turned on their master.

46:23.632 --> 46:26.133
Not so brilliant, huh, Dima?

46:29.660 --> 46:32.467
Ah, fuck.

46:32.506 --> 46:34.482
- Fritz,

46:34.516 --> 46:36.513
you used to work here, right?

46:36.557 --> 46:38.394
Where is the doctor?

46:38.434 --> 46:39.404
- Hey!

46:39.438 --> 46:42.075
Which way?

46:42.116 --> 46:44.285
<i>- Den Gleisen.</i>

46:44.326 --> 46:46.095
<i>Folgen.</i>

46:46.134 --> 46:47.835
- Dima,

46:47.875 --> 46:49.849
you can't be serious.

46:49.885 --> 46:52.190
You want to go to the base
of this thing?

46:52.228 --> 46:53.427
It's suicide.

46:53.467 --> 46:55.304
- I thought I made it clear.

46:55.342 --> 46:57.511
Our job is to find and capture
the doctor.

46:57.552 --> 46:58.818
- Or kill.

46:58.857 --> 47:00.295
Captured or killed, you said.

47:00.330 --> 47:02.329
- Yes, yes, yes.
Moscow wants him alive.

47:03.880 --> 47:04.942
- They're here!
- Go!

47:04.985 --> 47:06.012
Get out, Dima!

47:09.539 --> 47:11.376
Run, Dima!
For God's sakes!

47:15.466 --> 47:16.629
- Get in!

47:16.670 --> 47:18.507
Close the door!
Close the door!

47:24.774 --> 47:25.774
- Gun!

47:25.811 --> 47:26.811
- Get the fucking gun!

47:26.850 --> 47:27.850
- Go!
- Come on!

47:31.705 --> 47:33.737
Run faster!

47:33.781 --> 47:35.584
- Get in.

47:35.622 --> 47:37.757
- Close the door!

47:41.650 --> 47:43.088
- Come on, let's go!

47:43.123 --> 47:45.121
Forget the gun!
Get inside!

47:50.758 --> 47:53.257
- Lock it in, you fucking idiot!

47:59.664 --> 48:02.643
- What the fuck?

48:02.677 --> 48:03.807
- No, leave it!

48:03.849 --> 48:04.979
It can't hurt us.

48:10.412 --> 48:12.444
- This one can't hurt us.

48:21.494 --> 48:23.903
At last,
we're getting somewhere.

48:47.043 --> 48:48.607
<i>- Nein! Nein!</i>

48:48.650 --> 48:50.521
- Little fascist...

49:35.058 --> 49:36.861
- Sacha, go down there
and take a look.

49:36.901 --> 49:38.875
- What?
You crazy?

49:38.909 --> 49:40.712
- I've got a better idea.

49:40.750 --> 49:42.749
Vasja, get the boy.

49:42.793 --> 49:44.494
- Right.
In you go.

49:44.534 --> 49:45.732
<i>- Nein!</i>

49:45.773 --> 49:49.244
<i>- "Nein!
Nein!"</i>

49:49.290 --> 49:50.419
Come on.

49:52.872 --> 49:54.139
- Wait!

49:54.178 --> 49:55.810
First we'll take you down,

49:55.852 --> 49:58.019
then we'll bring you back.

49:58.062 --> 49:59.625
- In you go.

49:59.668 --> 50:02.443
<i>- Nein! Nein!</i>

50:05.160 --> 50:07.466
- I've got you!

50:07.504 --> 50:10.127
- Hans, tell me what you see!

