01:06:46.219 --> 01:06:47.445
- Here they are.

01:06:49.653 --> 01:06:52.051
- At least one is still alive.

01:06:52.087 --> 01:06:53.713
- Fuck you!
Fuck you!

01:06:53.754 --> 01:06:55.131
- Don't do this to me.
