- Listen.

01:08:02.104 --> 01:08:04.333
Listen!

01:08:04.372 --> 01:08:06.998
Can't you hear it?

01:08:07.038 --> 01:08:08.334
- What was that?

01:08:08.372 --> 01:08:10.839
- It's us, the Red Army,

01:08:10.873 --> 01:08:12.168
