01:13:09.323 --> 01:13:11.915
Okay.

01:13:11.957 --> 01:13:12.957
I think...

01:13:12.990 --> 01:13:14.580
Oh, shit.

01:13:14.623 --> 01:13:16.852
Shit, come on.

01:13:16.890 --> 01:13:19.221
Okay, that's fine.

01:13:31.925 --> 01:13:33.585
